Here is the straight text decoding of your server rules.

✨ Welcome to Gearblock! ✨
───── Server Rules ─────

➤ No griefing or stealing from other players.

➤ Respect all players and staff at all times.

➤ No cheating, hacks, or exploiting bugs.

➤ Keep chat clean and polite.

➤ No advertising other servers.

➤ Do not spam or annoy players.

➤ PvP allowed only in designated areas.

➤ Do not build inappropriate structures.

➤ Do not impersonate staff members.

➤ Use common sense and follow the server theme.

➤ Report issues or rule-breaking to staff.

➤ Do not abuse plugins or commands.

➤ Avoid excessive TNT for destructive actions.

➤ Keep farms and redstone builds contained.

➤ No stealing from community chests.

➤ Respect spawn and public areas.

➤ Do not sell items for real money.

➤ No inappropriate skins or usernames.

➤ Follow staff instructions immediately.

➤ Have fun, be creative, and enjoy Gearblock!
